## 10. Trampoline

One giant super-bouncy floor.

```scheme
(define (trampoline)
  (world/reset!)
  (world/gravity! 0 0.5)
  (world/floor! 240)
  (on-frame
   (lambda ()
     (when (input/pressed? 'a)
       (let ((b (world/spawn 'ball
                             (+ 20 (modulo (world/hash) 280)) 20)))
         (entity/shape! b 'circle 5)
         (entity/bounce! b 1.15)))    ;; super-bouncy!
     (world/step)
     (paint-clear)
     (world/each 'ball
                 (lambda (b) (paint-cell 'ball (entity/x b) (entity/y b) 5 5))))))
(big-bang trampoline)
```

